{"id":79183,"type":4,"name":"My Merry May with be","name_cn":"皋月物语","date":"2005-06-30","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/0b/fc/79183_K3KIk.jpg","rating":{"rank":123,"total":47,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":1,"7":5,"8":6,"9":14,"10":20},"score":8.9},"summary":"KID恋爱冒险名作《My Merry May》（中文译名为《五月恋爱》或《皋月物语》）系列在PS2平台上一共诞生三部作品，分另是：2003年1月30日发售的《My Merry May》；2003年4月24日发售的《My Merry Maybe》和2005年6月30日发售的《My Marry May with be》；\r\n但是，实际上独立故事的作品，也只有前面两款：《My Merry May》和《My Merry Maybe》，而2005年6月份KID在PS2上推出《With Be》版只是前两部作品的合集，就是把两款游戏整合在一起，添加数个结局和附加剧情后，再重新发售。但是两款作品都有一个共同点，就是都有一个以“人工生命体”（人工美少女）的人物为女主角，只是男主人公不一样罢了，时间上也有前后。如果玩家先玩过《My Merry May》后再去欣赏《My Merry Maybe》的话，对这部作品会有更深的感触。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>皋月物语</li><li><span>开发: </span><a href=\"/person/415\">KID</a></li><li><span>剧本: </span>長井知佳、<a href=\"/person/22479\">Q'tron</a>、<a href=\"/person/6973\">西川真音</a></li><li><span>音乐: </span><a href=\"/person/7337\">阿保剛</a></li><li><span>原画: </span><a href=\"/person/9803\">輿水隆之</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>MMMWB</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>マイ・メリー・メイ ウィズ ビー</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>五月恋爱物语</li><li><span>平台: </span>PS2</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PSP</li><li><span>游戏类型: </span>恋愛アドベンチャー</li><li><span>游玩人数: </span>1</li><li><span>发行日期: </span>2005年6月30日(PS2)</li><li><span>其他版本发行日期: </span>2010年3月25日(PSP)</li>","collection":{"on_hold":23,"dropped":1,"wish":395,"collect":62,"doing":25},"tags":[{"name":"KID","count":48},{"name":"galgame","count":41},{"name":"西川真音","count":22},{"name":"GAL","count":21},{"name":"PSP","count":11},{"name":"生肉","count":8},{"name":"ADV","count":7},{"name":"纯爱","count":6},{"name":"2005","count":6},{"name":"PC","count":5},{"name":"妹","count":3},{"name":"幼驯染","count":2},{"name":"PS2","count":2},{"name":"⊘日本","count":1},{"name":"☐","count":1},{"name":"ↈ","count":1},{"name":"9+","count":1},{"name":"全年龄","count":1},{"name":"AVG","count":1},{"name":"已下载","count":1},{